This repo is the modified unsecure initramfs with stock modules. the kernel
extraversion on these is -1193552 thats all you need to build a fully working
LI02 BASEBAND Kernel that will not remove the MEID from the device
as long as your using the LI02 kernel source. which can be found here and on 
http://opensource.samsung.com look up SCH-S720C and download the one ending 
in "UPDATE"1"
